parameters.query: SELECT p.id, p.sku, p.title, p.image_urls, p.brand, p.user_id, p.updated_at, COALESCE((SELECT vb.risk_level FROM vero_brands vb WHERE LOWER(p.brand) = LOWER(vb.brand_name) AND (vb.user_id = p.user_id OR vb.user_id IS NULL) LIMIT 1), 'none') as vero_risk FROM products_master p WHERE p.user_id = $1 AND p.image_urls IS NOT NULL AND jsonb_array_length(p.image_urls) > 0 AND (p.image_wash_status IS NULL OR p.image_wash_status = 'pending') $2 ORDER BY CASE WHEN p.brand IS NOT NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END, p.updated_at DESC LIMIT $3

parameters.query: UPDATE products_master SET image_urls = $1::jsonb, image_wash_status = 'completed', image_wash_type = $2, image_wash_at = NOW(), updated_at = NOW() WHERE id = $3 AND user_id = $4 AND updated_at = $5 RETURNING id, sku
INSERT INTO image_processing_history (user_id, product_id, sku, wash_type, original_count, processed_count, created_at) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, NOW())
DELETE FROM image_processing_history WHERE created_at < NOW() - INTERVAL '7 days'
